Common options:
--mode                          string   *  running mode, which has its own options
--help                                      flag to print usage help to stderr and exit
--clog-file                     string      path to file for log stream redirection
--version                                   flag to print version number to stderr and exit

Available running modes:
--mode get-balls-from-atoms-file
--mode calculate-vertices
--mode calculate-vertices-in-parallel
--mode calculate-contacts
--mode query-contacts
